(ISE Coursework Artifact: replication.pdf) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Goal) Tj
T*
(Replicate all reported experiments and statistical tests from raw datasets.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Exact replication steps) Tj
T*
(1\) Set up environment) Tj
T*
(   python3.11 -m venv .venv) Tj
T*
(   source .venv/bin/activate) Tj
T*
(   pip install -r requirements.txt) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2\) Run full pipeline) Tj
T*
(   .venv/bin/python run_pipeline.py --projects pytorch tensorflow keras incubator-mxnet ) Tj
T*
(caffe --repeats 30 --test-size 0.3 --max-features 1000 --seed-base 0) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3\) Verify generated files) Tj
T*
(   Expected per-project files:) Tj
T*
(   - results/<project>_NB.csv) Tj
T*
(   - results/<project>_LR.csv) Tj
T*
(   - results/<project>_combined_results.csv) Tj
T*
(   - results/<project>_wilcoxon_test.csv) Tj
T*
(   - results/<project>_NB_pos_f1.npy) Tj
T*
(   - results/<project>_LR_pos_f1.npy) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(   Expected cross-project files:) Tj
T*
(   - results/all_projects_combined_results.csv) Tj
T*
(   - results/all_projects_wilcoxon_test.csv) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Determinism and randomness) Tj
T*
(- Data shuffling uses fixed random state 999.) Tj
T*
(- Train/test split seeds are deterministic per repeat: seed_base + repeat index.) Tj
T*
(- For Logistic Regression, random_state is set per repeat.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Hardware/runtime note) Tj
T*
(- Runtime depends on CPU and dataset size.) Tj
T*
(- The baseline model uses 5-fold GridSearchCV inside each repeat and may take longer.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Troubleshooting) Tj
T*
(- If NLTK stopwords are unavailable, the tool automatically uses a built-in fallback list.) Tj
T*
(- If scipy import fails, reinstall dependencies using requirements.txt.) Tj
T*
